# Personal Health Assistant — Project Analysis

## Overview

A **full-stack Personal Health Assistant** web application built with three independent services:

| Tier | Technology | Port |
|------|-----------|------|
| **Frontend** | React 19 + Vite 7 + Tailwind CSS 4 | `5173` (dev) |
| **Backend** | Express 5 + MongoDB (Mongoose 9) | `5000` |
| **AI Service** | FastAPI (Python) + Google Gemini 2.5 Flash | `8000` |

---

## Architecture Diagram

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph Frontend["Frontend (React + Vite)"]
        UI[UI Components]
        SVC[Service Layer]
    end

    subgraph Backend["Backend (Express + MongoDB)"]
        AUTH[Auth Routes]
        API[API Routes]
        MW[JWT Middleware]
        DB[(MongoDB)]
    end

    subgraph AI["AI Service (FastAPI)"]
        RG[Recipe Graph]
        QG[Question Graph]
        GEM[Gemini 2.5 Flash]
    end

    UI --> SVC
    SVC --> AUTH
    SVC --> API
    AUTH --> MW --> DB
    API --> DB
    API --> AI
    RG --> GEM
    QG --> GEM
```

---

## Frontend — React 19 + Vite + Tailwind 4

### Key Dependencies
`react-router-dom` (routing), `axios` (HTTP), `framer-motion` (animations), `recharts` (charts), `tailwindcss` v4

### Pages & Routing

| Route | Component | Description |
|-------|-----------|-------------|
| `/` | `GetStarted` | Landing / splash page |
| `/auth` | `Auth` | Login & registration |
| `/forgot-password` | `ForgotPassword` | Password recovery via OTP |
| `/questionnaire` ★ | `Questionnaire` | Static onboarding health questions |
| `/ai-questions` ★ | `AIQuestions` | AI-generated follow-up questions |
| `/dashboard` ★ | `Dashboard` (39 KB) | Main dashboard with health metrics |
| `/exercise` ★ | `Exercise` | Exercise tracking (stub — 108 bytes) |
| `/skin-care` ★ | `SkinCare` | Skincare advice (stub — 110 bytes) |
| `/recipes` ★ | `Recipes` (49 KB) | Image-based recipe generator |
| `/chatbot` ★ | `Chatbot` (31 KB) | AI health chatbot |
| `/diet` ★ | `Diet` (42 KB) | Diet logging & tracking |
| `/activity` ★ | `Activity` (16 KB) | Daily activity logging |
| `/leaderboard` ★ | `Leaderboard` (29 KB) | Gamification leaderboard |

> ★ = Protected routes (requires JWT login)

### Frontend Services (API Wrappers)

| Service | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| [authService.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/frontend/src/services/authService.js) | Login, register, OTP handling |
| [profileService.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/frontend/src/services/profileService.js) | User profile CRUD |
| [chatService.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/frontend/src/services/chatService.js) | Chatbot interactions |
| [dietService.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/frontend/src/services/dietService.js) | Diet plan management |
| [activityService.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/frontend/src/services/activityService.js) | Activity logging |
| [gamificationService.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/frontend/src/services/gamificationService.js) | Points / leaderboard |

### Other Features
- **Dark/Light theme** toggle via `ThemeContext` (persisted to `localStorage`)
- **Protected routes** via `ProtectedRoute` component
- **Sidebar + MainLayout** shell for authenticated pages

