## Backend — Express 5 + MongoDB

### Key Dependencies
`express` v5, `mongoose` v9, `jsonwebtoken`, `bcrypt`, `@google/generative-ai`, `groq-sdk`, `multer`, `nodemailer`, `dotenv`, `cors`

### Entry Point: [index.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/backend/index.js)
- Connects to MongoDB via `MONGO_URI` env var
- Serves static uploads from `/uploads`
- Mounts 8 route groups under `/api`

### Route Files

| File | Mount | Purpose |
|------|-------|---------|
| [authRoutes.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/backend/routes/authRoutes.js) | `/api/auth` | Register, login, OTP, password reset |
| [profileRoutes.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/backend/routes/profileRoutes.js) | `/api` | User profile get/update |
| [aiRoutes.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/backend/routes/aiRoutes.js) | `/api` | AI proxy to Gemini/Groq |
| [recipeRoutes.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/backend/routes/recipeRoutes.js) (15 KB) | `/api` | Recipe CRUD, image upload → AI recipe gen |
| [chatbotRoutes.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/backend/routes/chatbotRoutes.js) (7 KB) | `/api` | Health chatbot with history |
| [dietRoutes.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/backend/routes/dietRoutes.js) (5 KB) | `/api` | Diet plan management |
| [activityRoutes.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/backend/routes/activityRoutes.js) (7 KB) | `/api` | Daily activity logging & streaks |
| [gamificationRoutes.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/backend/routes/gamificationRoutes.js) | `/api` | Points, streaks, leaderboard |

### Data Models (Mongoose)

| Model | Key Fields |
|-------|-----------|
| [User.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/backend/models/User.js) | fullname, email, password, healthProfile (age, gender, goals, diet type, skin type, etc.), aiQuestions[], gamification stats |
| [Diet.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/backend/models/Diet.js) | User's diet plans |
| [DailyActivity.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/backend/models/DailyActivity.js) | Daily activity records |
| [HealthChat.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/backend/models/HealthChat.js) | Chatbot conversation history |
| [RecipeChat.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/backend/models/RecipeChat.js) | Recipe generation history |
| [StarredRecipe.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/backend/models/StarredRecipe.js) | User's saved/starred recipes |
| [UploadLimit.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/backend/models/UploadLimit.js) | Image upload rate limiting |
| [Otp.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/backend/models/Otp.js) | OTP codes for password reset |

### Authentication
- **JWT-based** auth via [authMiddleware.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/backend/middleware/authMiddleware.js)
- Bearer token extracted from `Authorization` header
- Password hashing with `bcrypt`
- Email OTP for password recovery via `nodemailer`

