## Environment Variables Required

| Variable | Used By | Purpose |
|----------|---------|---------|
| `MONGO_URI` | Backend | MongoDB connection string |
| `JWT_SECRET` | Backend | JWT signing key |
| `GEMINI_API_KEY` | Backend + AI | Google Gemini API key |
| `GROQ_API_KEY` | Backend | Groq LLM API key (for chatbot) |
| Email config (SMTP) | Backend | Nodemailer for OTP emails |

