## Notable Observations

> [!TIP]
> **Large, Feature-Rich SPA** — The frontend has substantial page components (`Dashboard` at 39 KB, `Recipes` at 49 KB, `Diet` at 42 KB) indicating rich, interactive UIs with local state management.

> [!WARNING]
> **Stub Pages** — [Exercise.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/frontend/src/components/pages/Exercise.jsx) (108 bytes) and [SkinCare.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/frontend/src/components/pages/SkinCare.jsx) (110 bytes) are placeholder stubs not yet implemented.

> [!WARNING]
> **Syntax Error** — [photos.py](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/Ai-tasks/photos.py) line 2 has `COR+SMiddleware` instead of `CORSMiddleware`. This file appears to be a legacy version superseded by the LangGraph pipeline.

> [!NOTE]
> **Duplicate Static Serving** — [index.js](file:///c:/Users/Dell/Desktop/Mini%20Project/Code/backend/index.js) serves the `/uploads` directory twice (lines 29 and 42).

> [!NOTE]
> **No Tests** — No test files or test scripts were found in any tier of the project.

> [!NOTE]
> **No `.env` file committed** — Config uses `dotenv`, secrets must be provided via a `.env` file in both `backend/` and `Ai-tasks/`.

---

## How to Run

```bash
# 1. Backend (Express)
cd backend
npm install
# Create .env with MONGO_URI, JWT_SECRET, GEMINI_API_KEY, GROQ_API_KEY
node index.js              # → http://localhost:5000

# 2. Frontend (Vite + React)
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev                # → http://localhost:5173

# 3. AI Service (FastAPI)
cd Ai-tasks
pip install fastapi uvicorn langgraph langchain-google-genai google-generativeai pillow python-dotenv
# Create .env with GEMINI_API_KEY
uvicorn app:app --reload   # → http://localhost:8000
```
